  43,45,"wasal -ayha alrswl- 'atbae man 'arsalna min qablik min rusulina wahamlat shrayehm: aja't rusuluhum bieibadat ghyr allh? fa'iinahum ykhbrwnk 'ana dhlk lm yqe; f'in jmye alrusul daeawa 'iilaa ma dewt alnaas 'iilayh min eibadat allah whdh, la sharik lh, wnhawa ean eibadat ma siwaa allh"
