  44,9,"bl hwla' almushrikun fi shakin min alhq, fahum yalhun wylebwn, wala yusadiqun bh"
  44,10,"fantzr -ayha alrswl- bhwla' almushrikin yawm tati alsama' bidukhan mubin wadih yemm alnas, wyqal lhm: hdha eadhab mulim mwje, thuma yaqulun saylyn rafaeah wkshfh enhm: rabana akshif eanaa aledhab, fa'iina kshfth eanaa fa'iinaa muwminun bk"
  44,11,"fantzr -ayha alrswl- bhwla' almushrikin yawm tati alsama' bidukhan mubin wadih yemm alnas, wyqal lhm: hdha eadhab mulim mwje, thuma yaqulun saylyn rafaeah wkshfh enhm: rabana akshif eanaa aledhab, fa'iina kshfth eanaa fa'iinaa muwminun bk"
  44,12,"fantzr -ayha alrswl- bhwla' almushrikin yawm tati alsama' bidukhan mubin wadih yemm alnas, wyqal lhm: hdha eadhab mulim mwje, thuma yaqulun saylyn rafaeah wkshfh enhm: rabana akshif eanaa aledhab, fa'iina kshfth eanaa fa'iinaa muwminun bk"
  44,13,"kyf yakun lahum altdhkr walateaz baed nuzul aleadhab bhm, waqad ja'ahum rasul mbyn, wahu muhamad ealayh alsalat walslam, thuma 'aeraduu eanh wqalu: ellamh bashar 'aw alkhnt 'aw alshyatyn, hu majnun walays brswl?"
  44,14,"kyf yakun lahum altdhkr walateaz baed nuzul aleadhab bhm, waqad ja'ahum rasul mbyn, wahu muhamad ealayh alsalat walslam, thuma 'aeraduu eanh wqalu: ellamh bashar 'aw alkhnt 'aw alshyatyn, hu majnun walays brswl?"
  44,15,"snrfe eankum aleadhab qlyla, wstrwn 'anakum taeudun 'iilaa ma kuntum fih min alkufr waldalal waltkdhyb, wa'anana sneaqbkm ealaa dhlk"
  44,16,ywm nueadhib jmye alkufaar aleadhab al'akbar yawm alqiamat wahu yawm antqamna mnhm
  44,17,"wlqd akhtbrna wabtlyna qabl hwla' almushrikin qawm frewn, waja'ahum rasul krym, wahu musaa ealayh alslam, fakadhabuh fhlku, fhkdha nafeal baedayk 'ayuha alrswl, 'iin lam ywmnu"
  44,18,"wqal lahum mwsa: 'an sllimu 'ily eibad allah min bani 'iisrayiyl warslwhm mey; liaebuduu allah wahdah la sharik lh, 'iiniy lakum rasul 'amin ealaa wahyuh wrsalth"
  44,19,"wala ttkbru ealaa allah btkdhyb rslh, 'iiniy atikum bbrhan wadih ealaa sidq rsalty, 'iiniy astjrt biallah rabiy warabukum 'ana tqtlwny rjmana balhjart, wa'iin lam tsdqwny ealaa ma jitukum bih fkhllu sbyly, wkffu ean adhay"
  44,20,"wala ttkbru ealaa allah btkdhyb rslh, 'iiniy atikum bbrhan wadih ealaa sidq rsalty, 'iiniy astjrt biallah rabiy warabukum 'ana tqtlwny rjmana balhjart, wa'iin lam tsdqwny ealaa ma jitukum bih fkhllu sbyly, wkffu ean adhay"
  44,21,"wa'alla ttkbru ealaa allah btkdhyb rslh, 'iiniy atikum bbrhan wadih ealaa sidq rsalty, 'iiniy astjrt biallah rabiy warabukum 'ana tqtlwny rjmana balhjart, wa'iin lam tsdqwny ealaa ma jitukum bih fkhllu sbyly, wkffu ean adhay"
  44,22,fdea musaa rbh- hin kadhibuh fireawn waqawmuh walam yuminuu bh- qayla 'iina hwla' qawm mushrikun biallah kafrwn
  44,23,"f'asr- ya mwsa- bebady- aladhin saddaqwk, waminuu bk, watbewk, dun aladhin kadhabuk mnhm- laylana 'iinakum mutabaeun min fireawn wajunuduh ftnjwn, wyghrq fireawn wjnwdh"
  44,24,"watrk albahr kama hu ealaa halatih alty kan ealayha hin slkth, saknana ghyr mdtrb, 'iina fireawn wajunuduh mughraqun fi albhr"
  44,25,"km tarak fireawn waqawmuh baed muhlikuhum w'ighraq allah 'iiahum min basatin wajanaat nadrt, waeuyun min alma' jaryt, wazurue wamanazil jmylt, weysht kanuu fiha mtnemyn mtrfyn"
  44,26,"km tarak fireawn waqawmuh baed muhlikuhum w'ighraq allah 'iiahum min basatin wajanaat nadrt, waeuyun min alma' jaryt, wazurue wamanazil jmylt, weysht kanuu fiha mtnemyn mtrfyn"
  44,27,"km tarak fireawn waqawmuh baed muhlikuhum w'ighraq allah 'iiahum min basatin wajanaat nadrt, waeuyun min alma' jaryt, wazurue wamanazil jmylt, weysht kanuu fiha mtnemyn mtrfyn"
  44,28,"mthl dhlk aleiqab yeaqb allah man kdhdhab wbddal niemat allah kfrana, wa'awrathna tilk alnaeam min baed fireawn waqawmuh qwmana akharin khlfwhm min bani 'israyyl"
  44,29,"fma bakat alsama' wal'ard hznana ealaa fireawn wqwmh, wama kanuu mwkhkharyn ean aleuqubat alty hllat bhm"
  44,30,wlqd njjayna bani 'iisrayiyl min aleadhab almudhll lahum biqatl abnayhm waistikhdam nsayhm
  44,31,"mn frewn, 'iinah kan jbarana min almshrkyn, msrfana fi alelw waltkbr ealaa eibad allh"
  44,32,wlqd astafayna bani 'iisrayiyl ealaa eilm minaa bihim ealaa ealamiun zmanhm
  44,33,watynahm min almejzat ealaa yd musaa ma fih abtlawhm wakhtbarhm rukha'an wshdt
  44,34,"'iina hwla' almushrikin min qawmik -ayha alrswl- lyqwlwn: ma hi 'iilaa mawtatuna alty nmwtha, wahi almawtat al'uwlaa walakhyrt, wama nahn baed mmatna bimabeuthin llhsab walthwab waleqab"
  44,35,"'in hwla' almushrikin min qawmik -ayha alrswl- lyqwlwn: ma hi 'iilaa mawtatuna alty nmwtha, wahi almawtat al'uwlaa walakhyrt, wama nahn baed mmatna bimabeuthin llhsab walthwab waleqab"
