  45,30,"fama aladhin amanuu biallah warasulih fi aldnya, wamtthlu awamrh wajtanibuu nwahyh, fayudkhiluhum rabuhum fi janatah brhmth, dhlk aldukhul hu alfawz almubin aldhy la fawz bedh"
