  45,32,"w'idha qil lkm: 'iina waed allah bbeth alnaas min qbwrhm hq, walsaaeat la shaka fyha, qltm: maa nadri ma alsae? wama natawaqae wqweha 'iilaa twhmana, wama nahn bmthqqyn 'ana alssaeat atyt"
